Biography Intro: Johnson Akuchie (born January 6, 1990 in Lagos, Nigeria) is a Nigerian Association Football Forward currently playing for Flandria of the Primera B Metropolitana in Argentina.

NAME: Johnson Akuchie

DATE OF BIRTH: January 6, 1990

PLACE OF BIRTH: Lagos

OCCUPATION: Nigerian Association Football Forward currently playing for Flandria of the Primera B Metropolitana in Argentina.

CAREER AND PROFESSIONAL ACTIVITIES: Nigerian Association Football Forward currently playing for Flandria of the Primera B Metropolitana in Argentina.
